-- // Zynix FREE - Premium Roblox Cheat
-- // Completely rewritten, optimized, and feature-packed.
-- // Now includes CS:GO style Anti-Aim, improved Third Person, and robust combat/visuals/movement.

--[[
    PERFORMANCE NOTES:
    - RenderStepped handles Aimbot, FOV, Hitbox Visuals, Anti-Aim, and ESP.
      All of these are camera- or input-dependent and must update each frame.
    - Stepped is used for NoClip and Fullbright to avoid redundant checks.
    - Heartbeat is not used to keep the script simple; RenderStepped is sufficient
      as long as the loop is kept lightweight.
    - nil checks and pcall are used everywhere to prevent crashes.
    - Drawing objects are cached and only created when needed.
--]]

